     {"element":
      ["h2",
       true,
       [["id", "Loogle-Usage"], ["class", "markdown-heading"]],
       [{"text": "Loogle Usage"},
        {"text": " "},
        {"element":
         ["a",
          true,
          [["class", "hover-link"], ["href", "#Loogle-Usage"]],
          [{"text": "#"}]]}]]},
     {"element":
      ["p",
       true,
       [],
       [{"text": "Loogle finds definitions and lemmas in various ways:"}]]},
     {"element":
      ["p",
       true,
       [],
       [{"text": "By constant:"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text": "🔍 Real.sin"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text":
         "finds all lemmas whose statement somehow mentions the sine function."}]]},
     {"element":
      ["p",
       true,
       [],
       [{"text": "By lemma name substring:"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text": "🔍 "},
        {"text": "\""},
        {"text": "differ"},
        {"text": "\""},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text": "finds all lemmas that have "},
        {"text": "\""},
        {"text": "differ"},
        {"text": "\""},
        {"text": " somewhere in their lemma name."}]]},
     {"element":
      ["p",
       true,
       [],
       [{"text": "By subexpression:"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text": "🔍 _ * (_ ^ _)"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text":
         "finds all lemmas whose statements somewhere include a product where the second argument is raised to some power."}]]},
     {"element":
      ["p",
       true,
       [],
       [{"text": "The pattern can also be non-linear, as in"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text": "🔍 Real.sqrt ?a * Real.sqrt ?a"}]]},
     {"element":
      ["p",
       true,
       [],
       [{"text":
         "If the pattern has parameters, they are matched in any order. Both of these will find List.map:"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text": "🔍 (?a -> ?b) -> List ?a -> List ?b"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text": "🔍 List ?a -> (?a -> ?b) -> List ?b"}]]},
     {"element":
      ["p",
       true,
       [],
       [{"text": "By main conclusion:"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text": "🔍 |- tsum _ = _ * tsum _"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text":
         "finds all lemmas where the conclusion (the subexpression to the right of all → and ∀) has the given shape."}]]},
     {"element":
      ["p",
       true,
       [],
       [{"text":
         "As before, if the pattern has parameters, they are matched against the hypotheses of the lemma in any order; for example,"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text": "🔍 |- _ < _ → tsum _ < tsum _"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text":
         "will find tsum_lt_tsum even though the hypothesis f i < g i is not the last."}]]},
     {"element":
      ["p",
       true,
       [],
       [{"text":
         "If you pass more than one such search filter, separated by commas Loogle will return lemmas which match all of them. The search"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text": "🔍 Real.sin, "},
        {"text": "\""},
        {"text": "two"},
        {"text": "\""},
        {"text": ", tsum, _ * _, _ ^ _, |- _ < _ → _"},
        {"raw": "\n"},
        {"text":
         "would find all lemmas which mention the constants Real.sin and tsum, have "},
        {"text": "\""},
        {"text": "two"},
        {"text": "\""},
        {"text":
         " as a substring of the lemma name, include a product and a power somewhere in the type, and have a hypothesis of the form _ < _ (if there were any such lemmas). Metavariables (?a) are assigned independently in each filter."}]]},
     {"element":
      ["p",
       true,
       [],
       [{"text": "You can modify the Loogle server URL by setting the "},
        {"element":
         ["code", true, [], [{"text": "LEANSEARCHCLIENT_LOOGLE_API_URL"}]]},
        {"text": " environment variable."}]]}]]},
